'''Evitch Jenton''' was the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|governor]] of [[Ebra]]. During his rule, the export of [[lu-ramin]] from Ebra was heavily restricted. Though the native [[Ebranite]]s had formerly sold most of their lu-ramin to the [[Carosite]]s, Jenton's regime cut this trade off in favor of exclusive exports to Imperial-authorized corporations and cultures.

Imperial repression of the Ebranites went far beyond trade restrictions. Governor Jenton assumed absolute control over Ebran politics, supplanting the traditional clan-based government of the Ebranites. Any Ebranite suspected of seditious sentiments was exiled to the lu-ramin mines of [[Grythsorin]]. Hundreds of Ebranites took up arms against Imperial rule, becoming part of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

